<body>
  <h1>WHAT IS IT?</h1>
  <h2>CC Local Point is a project by <a href="https://pt-br.facebook.com/creativecommonsportugal/">Creative Commons Portugal</a> and <a href="https://www.dinamo10.net">DINAMO10</a> that aims to clarify basic copyright law and its relation to Creative Commons licensing and to promote the use of CC licenses as an alternative option for creative practice and business modelo development.</h2>
  <h2>Our purpose is to create contact points in creative hubs in order to reinforce their role as information centers for artists, makers and creative professionais.</h2>

  <div>
    <img src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/101953881/185510515-960697a2-4cd1-40aa-812c-b508b2c7c558.png" alt="CCLP Aims" width="2000">
  </div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="column1">
